    "seoTitle": "Best HR Software 2026: Ranked by Trust Score, Integration & Full Employee Lifecycle Coverage",
    "metaDescription": "The best HR software in 2026, ranked by Trust Score, Integration Score, and employee lifecycle coverage. We tested 25+ HRIS platforms to find the people tools that actually work.",
