    "seoTitle": "Best Employee Performance Management Software 2026: Ranked for Culture & Real Impact",
    "metaDescription": "The best employee performance management software in 2026, ranked by cultural impact, Trust Score, and Integration Score. Find the platform that turns performance reviews into actual development.",
